dct_title_s: San Luis Obispo Bay and Port Harford, California
dct_alternative_sm: San Luis Obispo Bay and approaches
dct_description_sm: U.S. Coast and Geodetic Survey ; F.M. Thorn, superintendent ; verified: B.A. Colonna, assistant in charge of office.
Relief shown by contours and spot heights; depths shown by soundings.
"Topography by L.A. Sengteller ... 1871 and 1872. Hydrography by ... L.A. Sengteller, Lieuts. E.H.C. Lautze and E.D. Taussig ... between 1875 and 1884.
Oriented with north toward upper right.
Includes tables and notes on soundings, tides, lighthouses, and buoys.
